{"word":"δαμάω","slug":"δαμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n23385\" key=\"dama/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">δᾰμάω</orth>, a form assumed as the <per opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"per\">1st pers.</per> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δαμᾷ, δαμάᾳ, δαμόωσι,</foreign> which in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> are <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δαμάζω</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δάμνημι</foreign>: but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δαμόωσι, δαμόωνται,</foreign> are <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> in late <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2046.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:247\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Q.S.\">Q.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.247</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2046.tlg001.perseus-grc1:249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">249</biblScope></bibl>.</entryFree>"}]}